  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c72c9706ba29a9d428084a4a0a43db7f, type: 3}
  m_Name: DialogueObject
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueObject
  dialogue:
  - 'As you can see the damage is quite extensive.


    All the more reason to find
    the fool behind this mess. If you give me the go-ahead I can expand the search
    to the whole network.


    <i>Sounds of splashing may be heard as Rivera runs
    up to you and Parker looking mortified about the state of the sewer.</i>'
  - "Oh This is terrible!!! This is doing irreversible damage to the water system!\n
    \nAdvisor! We need to get to removing this toxic goop immediately. The waste
    will contaminate the water system if we do not act immediatelly!"
  - line 3
